metadata.name: Metamorphose
metadata.description:
I guess all artist, or all the people who create have this moment,
Like moving to new phase, where their style changed from what it was to what it is now
Usually it happen after long time creating in the same style, successfully
Suddenly they creating different, different "art" because they changed,
they don't see beauty the same, or their drive is not the same...
Or who the fuck know

Usually people that love what they used to create and do will not understand what happen
What changed, why his work is different
And they will drop and leave

But some will stay and new one will come along,
Because they understand the metamorphose
And they curios where it will lead to

Well fuck
I guess it happen not only to artist
I guess it happens to all of us
Its called growth
